## Security Properties

Properties are security/correctness claims checked against function behavior.

| Property | Summary |
|----------|---------|
| [rotationEquivalenceRelationsHold — Rotation Equivalence Relations Hold](properties/misc.md#rotationequivalencerelationshold--rotation-equivalence-relations-hold) | Rotation equivalence relations hold: asserts `ROTL`{n} x == ROTR`{(w - n) % w} x` and `ROTR`{n} x == ROTL`{(w - n) % w} x` for all `x`. |
| [hexDigitsEncodeCorrectly — Hex Digits Encode Correctly](properties/misc.md#hexdigitsencodecorrectly--hex-digits-encode-correctly) | Hex digits encode correctly: asserts `0x7 == 0b0111` and `0xa == 0b1010`. |
| [wordsEncodeCorrectly — Words Encode Correctly](properties/misc.md#wordsencodecorrectly--words-encode-correctly) | Words encode correctly: asserts `0xa103fe23 == 0b10100001000000111111111000100011` and `0xa103fe2332ef301a == 0b1010000100000011111111100010001100110010111011110011000000011010`. |
| [integersEncodeCorrectly — Integers Encode Correctly](properties/misc.md#integersencodecorrectly--integers-encode-correctly) | Integers encode correctly: asserts `291 == 0x00000123`. |
